UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Located in the heart of the hustle, Coffee and the City is your ultimate urban sanctuary. We blend the fast-paced energy of the metropolis with the slow, deliberate art of brewing the perfect cup. It is the ideal pitstop for the busy professional needing a spark or the dreamer watching the world go by through our panoramic windows. Our menu features bold espresso blends designed to energise you, as well as velvety lattes perfect for a rainy afternoon. More than just a caffeine fix, we offer a slice of city life, served in a cup.'
WHERE name = 'Coffee and the City';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Kashtan Coffee is a nostalgic embrace of timeless traditions and soulful atmospheres. Stepping inside feels like visiting a stylish, retro era where vinyl records spin softly in the background, and the aroma of freshly baked cheesecake fills the air. We pride ourselves on sourcing high-quality beans that are roasted to perfection, highlighting comforting, chocolatey, and nutty notes. It is a space designed for deep conversations, chess games, and slowing down time. Whether you are hidden away in our courtyard or enjoying the cozy interior, Kashtan offers a genuine sense of community and warmth in every single cup.'
WHERE name = 'Kashtan Coffee';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'True to our name, Something Interesting is not just a coffee shop; it is a destination for curiosity and creativity. Tucked away from the predictable main streets, we combine an artisanal gallery experience with top-tier specialty coffee. Here, visual art meets the art of the barista in a seamless blend of aesthetics and flavour. Expect the unexpected, from our eclectic decor and handcrafted ceramics to signature seasonal drinks that challenge the conventional palette. It is the ideal spot for inspiration seekers looking for a quiet corner to think or a unique environment to share with friends.'
WHERE name = 'Something Interesting';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Black Honey is the ultimate destination for the modern coffee purist. We approach coffee with scientific precision and artistic passion, focusing strictly on the clarity of flavour and the journey of the bean. Our minimalist, monochrome interior eliminates distractions, allowing you to focus entirely on the sensory experience of your drink. From bright, fruity pour-overs to rich, full-bodied espresso, our rotating selection of single-origin beans ensures there is always something new to explore. We believe in transparency and quality, serving a cup that is as bold, clean, and uncompromising as our aesthetic.'
WHERE name = 'Black Honey';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Beige Bistro is a celebration of slow living, soft tones, and comforting flavours. Blending the casual elegance of a European bistro with the warmth of a neighbourhood cafe, we create a space that feels like a gentle hug. Our focus extends beyond excellent coffee to include a curated menu of fresh pastries, wholesome brunches, and light bites that pair perfectly with your brew. The aesthetic is calm and airy, filled with natural light and textures that invite you to linger. It is the perfect backdrop for a lazy Sunday morning or a relaxed midday break.'
WHERE name = 'Beige Bistro';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Makers Coffee is built on the philosophy that great coffee is created by hand, heart, and a dedication to the craft. We view our shop as a community hub for creators and enthusiasts alike, offering a space that is as inspiring as the beverage in your cup. Our minimalist interior serves as a blank canvas for your thoughts, while our baristas work with precision to highlight the unique profiles of every bean. Whether you are collaborating on a new project or enjoying a solitary moment of focus, Makers provides a refined, distraction-free environment where quality is the only standard.'
WHERE name = 'Makers Coffee';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Octo Tower represents a new perspective on coffee culture, literally raising the bar for your daily ritual. Housed within a unique architectural landmark, our multi-level space offers more than just exceptional caffeine; it provides panoramic views and a distinct sense of escape from the street-level rush. We combine the functionality of a modern workspace with the soul of a specialty coffee bar, creating a vertical journey of taste. Each floor offers a different energy, from buzzing social hubs to quiet corners for deep thought. Come for the signature brews and fresh-baked goods, but stay for the inspiring atmosphere that invites you to see the city differently.'
WHERE name = 'Octo Tower';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Foundation Coffee Roasters stands as a pillar of the specialty coffee movement, grounded in a deep respect for the entire supply chain. As a dedicated roastery and café, we believe that the true foundation of a great cup lies in transparency, ethical sourcing, and scientific precision. Our industrial-chic space allows you to witness the roasting process firsthand, bridging the gap between the raw bean and your beverage. We offer an extensive menu ranging from classic espresso-based drinks to experimental brewing methods. It is a place for connoisseurs and curious beginners alike to discover the complex, rich potential of coffee in its purest form.'
WHERE name = 'Foundation Coffee Roasters';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Daily is designed to be the most reliable and delightful part of your routine. We believe that your everyday coffee ritual should never be mundane; it should be a moment of quiet luxury and consistency. Our approach focuses on warmth and hospitality, serving high-quality specialty coffee without any pretension. The atmosphere is tuned to the rhythm of the city — energising in the morning and relaxing in the afternoon. With a carefully curated selection of beans and a menu of comfort food favourites, Daily is your neighbourhood anchor, a place where the staff knows your name and your order is always perfect.'
WHERE name = 'Daily';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Lou Lou brings a touch of Parisian charm and effortless elegance to the local coffee scene. More than just a café, it is a sensory experience defined by soft aesthetics, delicate pastries, and beautifully presented drinks. Our space is inspired by the classic European bistro, inviting you to slow down and savour the sweeter moments of life. We pair our specialty coffee with an exquisite selection of artisanal desserts and light bites, making it the perfect destination for a romantic date or a treat-yourself afternoon. At Lou Lou, we believe in beauty, flavour, and the joy of sharing a table with people you love.'
WHERE name = 'Lou Lou';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Doubledecker offers a charming slice of London right in the city centre, inviting guests into a space defined by English heritage and warmth. The two-story layout allows you to choose between the bustling energy of the ground floor or the elevated tranquillity of the upper level, which features panoramic windows perfect for people-watching. We are renowned for our artisanal approach to baking, with a display case constantly filled with towering slices of carrot cake, rich red velvet, and seasonal tarts. It is a place where classic aesthetics meet comfort, making it the perfect backdrop for a long conversation over a pot of tea or a perfectly brewed cappuccino.'
WHERE name = 'DoubleDecker Cake & Coffee';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'White Coffee Bar is a sanctuary for minimalists and purists who believe that clarity in design leads to clarity in flavour. Our interior is a study in "white magic"—a bright, airy space filled with natural light, botanical accents, and clean lines that refresh the senses. We focus on third-wave coffee culture, offering meticulously sourced beans and alternative brewing methods that highlight delicate flavour notes. It is a social hub where the buzz of conversation blends with the hiss of the espresso machine, creating an atmosphere that is both energising and aesthetically pleasing. Whether you are here to work or socialise, the environment encourages a fresh perspective.'
WHERE name = 'White Coffeebar';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Holy Bun is the embodiment of "hygge" and comfort food, designed to feel like a welcoming home away from home. The interior draws on Scandinavian simplicity with soft textures and warm lighting, but the real heart of the shop is the open kitchen and the bakery. We are famous for our freshly baked goods, particularly our signature cinnamon buns and flaky almond croissants that pair perfectly with a strong morning brew. It is a spot for slow mornings and indulgent brunches, where the smell of warm dough and spices greets you at the door. Every visit feels like a hug, offering a sweet escape from the daily grind.'
WHERE name = 'Holy Bun';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Chorna Kishka (Black Cat White Cat) is a soulful destination for true coffee aficionados who appreciate a blend of cozy atmosphere and professional expertise. As a staple of the local third-wave coffee scene, we pride ourselves on serving 100% Arabica beans and offering a wide range of alternative brewing methods like Chemex and V60. The vibe is friendly, urban, and unpretentious, often buzzing with a creative crowd. We balance high-quality caffeine with a relaxed, "living room" feel, making it an easy place to settle in for hours. It is the kind of spot where the baristas know their craft deeply and are always happy to guide you toward your new favourite blend.'
WHERE name = 'Chorna Kishka';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Pan Zavarkin & Son is far more than a coffee shop; it is a time machine disguised as a café and museum. Located in a historic building with a rich past, the interior transports you back to the early 20th century with its collection of antique clocks, vintage samovars, and retro decor. The air is thick with the history of the original colonial goods store, and our staff often adds to the immersion with period-appropriate attire. We offer an extensive selection of rare teas and classic coffees, best enjoyed alongside a traditional dessert. It is a unique cultural experience where the ticking of a hundred clocks reminds you to savour the present moment.'
WHERE name = 'Pan Zavar\'kin ta Syn';

UPDATE cafes
SET description = 'Lviv Croissants brings the reliable, bustling energy of a beloved national bakery to Vinnytsia, serving as a go-to spot for freshness and variety. The concept focuses on the art of the large, freshly baked croissant, which serves as the base for dozens of creative culinary combinations. Whether you are craving a savoury lunch packed with meats and veggies or a sweet treat overflowing with chocolate and fruit, everything is prepared right before your eyes. The atmosphere is always lively and fast-paced, making it an ideal pitstop for a quick, satisfying meal that never compromises on taste or quality.'
WHERE name = 'Lviv Croissants';
